pages.text: Ars Nouveau 1.9.6 $(li)Increases the delay time. $(li)Nerfs crop growth for condensers, buffs mob death.$(li)Added support for modded inventories for Carbuncles and Summoning Crystals.$(li)Blink can now warp entities when holding a warp scroll.$(li)Runes can now deposit items into adjacent inventories when using Item Pickup. $(li)Fixes breeding not counting for the condenser

$(li)Spell Turrets and Whelps can now use Exchange$(li)Fixes lighting on the Wand$(li)Projectiles now spawn particles further from your face$(li)Adds Archwood Wood$(li)Blink has been reworked and will now warp you on the sides of blocks, or up blocks if needed
